e basics of product framing and positioning and introduce a process you can use to find your own products best frame. Tickets prices depend on the size of the group. If you want to organize one in your town, drop me a line.</span></p>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#191919\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" disabled=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Inboundcon-backstage-3.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" admin_label=\"Image\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_width=\"1px\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" gutter_width=\"3\" custom_margin=\"|||\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"on\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"on\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"on\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"on\" admin_label=\"row\" disabled=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" disabled=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" admin_label=\"Text\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_padding=\"25px|25px|25px|25px\" disabled=\"off\"]<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Private half-day framing workshop</b></span><span class=\"s2\"><b> ($2K + travel)</b></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p3\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\">I come to your office and spend a half day working with your team.&nbsp;</span>The schedule for the day looks like this.</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>9:00&ndash;9:20&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </b></span><span class=\"s2\">Introduction to product framing and positioning including why we stink at it</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>9:20-10:00 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </b></span><span class=\"s2\">A walkthrough of the framing process including the inputs and outputs</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:00&ndash;10:30 &nbsp; &nbsp; </b></span><span class=\"s2\">De-framing: a discussion of the current product frame and&nbsp;</span><span class=\"s2\">how to de-frame that product</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:30- 11:00 </b>&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class=\"s2\">An interactive discussion working through the long list of the&nbsp;</span><span class=\"s2\">company&rsquo;s unique attributes</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>11:00 &ndash; 11:30</b> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class=\"s2\">Value &ndash; we then work through the value that is mapped to the&nbsp;</span>unique attributes</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>11:30 - 12:00</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; Positionstorming &ndash; working with the 4 styles of framing as a guide we will brainstorm a long list of potential &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; frames for consideration</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:15 &ndash; 12:45</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;Creating the short list. We will narrow down the long list of potential frames to a short list of candidates</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45 &ndash; 1:00 &nbsp;</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;Next steps &ndash; I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#000000\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" gutter_width=\"3\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" background_color_2=\"#ffffff\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"on\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"on\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"on\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"on\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-top:20px;\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/InounbCON-level.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" animation=\"left\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" custom_margin=\