 framing and positioning including why we stink at it</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>9:20-10:00    </b></span><span class=\"s2\">A walkthrough of the framing process including the inputs and outputs</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:0010:30   </b></span><span class=\"s2\">De-framing: a discussion of the current product frame and</span><span class=\"s2\">how to de-frame that product</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:30- 11:00 </b>  </span><span class=\"s2\">An interactive discussion working through the long list of the</span><span class=\"s2\">companys unique attributes</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>11:00  11:30</b>   </span><span class=\"s2\">Value  we then work through the value that is mapped to the</span>unique attributes</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>11:30 - 12:00</strong>   Positionstorming  working with the 4 styles of framing as a guide we will brainstorm a long list of potential               frames for consideration</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:15  12:45</strong>  Creating the short list. We will narrow down the long list of potential frames to a short list of candidates</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45  1:00 </strong>  Next steps  I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#000000\" button_use_icon=\"on