<b>9:20-10:00 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </b></span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">A walkthrough of the framing process including the inputs and outputs</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:00&ndash;10:30 &nbsp; &nbsp; </b></span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">De-framing: a discussion of the current product frame and&nbsp;</span><span class=\"s2\">how to de-frame that product</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:30- 11:00 </b>&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">An interactive discussion working through the long list of the&nbsp;</span><span class=\"s2\">company&rsquo;s unique attributes</span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>11:00 &ndash; 11:30</b> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">Value &ndash; we then work through the value that is mapped to the&nbsp;</span>unique attributes</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>11:30 - 12:00</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Positionstorming &ndash; working with the 4 styles of framing as a guide we will brainstorm a long list of potential frames for consideration</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:15 &ndash; 12:45</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Creating the short list. We will narrow down the long list of potential frames to a short list of candidates</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45 &ndash; 1:00 </strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Next steps &ndash; I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#000000\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;||bottom:25px;||width:170px;\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" gutter_width=\"3\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" background_color_2=\"#ffffff\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"on\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"on\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"on\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"on\" disabled=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" disabled=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/InounbCON-level.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_width=\"1px\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" disabled=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"25px|25px|25px|25px\" disabled=\"off\"]<p