span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:0010:30   </b></span></span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">De-framing: a discussion of the current product frame and</span><span class=\"s2\">how to de-frame that product</span></span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>10:30- 11:00 </b>  </span></span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">An interactive discussion working through the long list of the</span><span class=\"s2\">companys unique attributes</span></span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>11:00  11:30</b>   </span></span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">Value  we then work through the value that is mapped to the</span>unique attributes</span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>11:30 - 12:00</strong>   </span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Positionstorming  working with the 4 styles of framing as a guide we will brainstorm a long list of potential frames for consideration</span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:15  12:45</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Creating the short list. We will narrow down the long list of potential frames to a short list of candidates</span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45  1:00 </strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Next steps  I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></h4>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button 