   </span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Positionstorming  working with the 4 styles of framing as a guide we will brainstorm a long list of potential frames for consideration</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:15  12:45</strong></span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Creating the short list. We will narrow down the long list of potential frames to a short list of candidates</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45  1:00 </strong></span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Next steps  I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></h4>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#000000\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;||bottom:25px;||width:170px;\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"2\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" background_color_2=\"#ffffff\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"on\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"on\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"on\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"on\" admin_label=\"row\" disabled=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" disabled=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/InounbCON-level.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"